Package org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.ui

This package contains bean classes used by the active bpel WAR.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AeComponent Base component for a user interface widget.
AeContainer AeContainer UI widget acts as a container to hold AeComponent objects using the composite pattern.
AeFlowLayoutManager Implements a simple layout based on the left to right flow layout algorithm.
AeGraphContainer Basic figure container that is the root level container for all of the figure components.
AeIcon A component used to display an image.
AeIconLabel Draws a text label with an icon on the left.
AeLayoutManagerAdopter Adaptor for the AWT LayoutManager2 interface.
AeTextLabel Renders a text label.
AeUIUtil Utility methods used for the UI components.
AeXyLayoutManager Implements a arbitrary coordinate based layout mechanism..
